0) Notation

AIOc: 18-decimal governance/treasury token (base unit = 10^-18 AIOc).

TVL$: 30-day TWAP of system value at risk (USD).

t: quorum threshold of oracles required to finalize a price (e.g., 4 for 4-of-7).

