1) Set MDP$ by TVL and Liquidity (no guesswork at runtime)

Formula (pick the tighter bound):

Liquidity-bounded: MDP$_liq = α × TVL$ with α = 0.25 (25%)

Depth-bounded: MDP$_depth = min over venues of (γ × 24h Notional) with γ = 0.5

Select: MDP$ = min( MDP$_liq, MDP$_depth ), but clamped to [$1M, $100M] for Phase-1


