3) Convert to per-operator bond (what each oracle must post)

We want t operators to lose at least SF × MDP$ (in USD value) if they collude.

Per-operator bond (USD):

B_op$ ≥ (SF × MDP$) / t

Then denominate in AIOc:

B_op(AIOc) = max( B_floor(AIOc),  B_op$ / Price(AIOc)$ )

Floors (Phase-1):

